1
00:00:03,340 --> 00:00:05,710
Sorry to bother you when you're so busy.

2
00:00:06,380 --> 00:00:07,720
No, not at all.

3
00:00:08,170 --> 00:00:10,890
Actually, I also wanted to get
your advice on something.

4
00:00:11,140 --> 00:00:13,350
But you go first. What's going on?

5
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:15,220
Huh?

6
00:00:16,270 --> 00:00:19,230
I thought you came here
because of some emergency.

7
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:21,190
Makoto...

8
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:24,700
You're way too nice.

9
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:26,650
Thank you.

10
00:00:26,650 --> 00:00:28,150
But it's not what you think.

11
00:00:28,150 --> 00:00:30,740
I wanted to ask about the two of you.

12
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:32,490
The two of us?

13
00:00:32,490 --> 00:00:35,370
You and Yuki, of course.

14
00:00:35,370 --> 00:00:37,450
Did you hear something?

15
00:00:37,910 --> 00:00:40,710
Like, if he's fallen for someone else?

16
00:00:40,870 --> 00:00:42,290
Huh?

17
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:46,600
No, it seems like he likes someone else.

18
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:49,510
He's been avoiding me.

19
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:52,140
Oh...

20
00:00:53,180 --> 00:00:54,890
I think I get it now.

21
00:00:55,100 --> 00:00:57,350
Anyway, it looks like everything's fine.

22
00:00:57,350 --> 00:00:58,770
I'll let you two talk it out.

23
00:00:58,980 --> 00:01:00,600
He's on his way here.

24
00:01:00,890 --> 00:01:02,150
Yuki?!

25
00:01:02,510 --> 00:01:03,690
You asked him to come here too?

26
00:01:03,690 --> 00:01:04,810
Of course!

27
00:01:04,810 --> 00:01:08,070
Wait, I'm not
mentally prepared for this...

28
00:01:08,070 --> 00:01:10,070
Oh, but before he gets here,

29
00:01:10,610 --> 00:01:12,570
there's something else I want to discuss.

30
00:01:14,610 --> 00:01:17,450
It's about our anniversary...

31
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,460
Honestly, what a handful
these two are.

32
00:01:22,790 --> 00:01:24,960
Um, excuse me.

33
00:01:32,260 --> 00:01:34,840
(Why is Makoto here?)
